arts.ttl: Leo Duru and Aaron Pressley score first Barrow goals in win over Accrington
arts.sum: The contest turned on a superb save from Paul Farman 20 minutes from time.

Barrow's impressive 2-1 win away to Notts County on Tuesday night ended three straight defeats in the league. Accrington's 2-0 win against MK Dons was their second win in their last three games. Bar...
